DECLARE @STARTDATETIME datetime2 = SYSDATETIME()
DECLARE @DEALTIME_1 float

IF OBJECT_ID(N'dbo.YellowTaxi_Test1', N'U') IS NOT NULL DROP TABLE  [dbo].[YellowTaxi_Test1]
SELECT TOP 10000 * INTO [dbo].[YellowTaxi_Test1] FROM [dbo].[YellowTaxi]
OPTION(MAXDOP 1)

set @DEALTIME_1 = (SELECT DATEDIFF(MILLISECOND, @STARTDATETIME, SYSDATETIME()) AS PROCESSING_TIME_MS);

SELECT N'処理①：' + Format(@DEALTIME_1, '#,###') + N'ms'
        + N'（' + Format(@DEALTIME_1/1000, '#,###.###') + N's）'
